Key Match Events: Freddy Peralta pitched six scoreless innings.
William Contreras hit a two-run homer in the fifth inning.
Devin Williams secured a 1-2-3 ninth inning for his sixth save in seven chances.
Jackson Chourio's RBI base single started the scoring.
Blake Perkins hit a two-run double.
Michael Conforto hit a run-scoring double.
Heliot Ramos added a run with a base hit in the eighth inning.
Miscellaneous Highlights: Giants' C Patrick Bailey could be activated from the 10-day injured list on Thursday.
Brewers' LHP Hoby Milner looks to begin a rehab assignment on Aug. 30.
